name: Corporal Derdram (V)
Lore: 'Member of Imperial Intelligence, Internal Security division. Assigned by IntSec to Executor. Responsible for physical safety of Imperial personnel against Rebel saboteurs.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at an Executor site, may use 1 Force to place a just lost non-unique smuggler (and all copies of that card in opponent''s Lost Pile) out of play. At same non-docking bay site, opponent may not deploy Jar Jar or spies.',
